{
  "config": {
    "wide_screen_mode": true,
    "enable_forward": true
  },
  "header": {
    "title": {
      "tag": "plain_text",
      "content": "LiYe Verdict · {{decision_badge}}"
    },
    "template": "{{header_template}}"
  },
  "elements": [
    {
      "tag": "markdown",
      "content": "**Trace ID**：`{{trace_id}}`\n\n**Decision**：**{{decision}}**\n\n**Origin**：`{{origin}}`  ·  **Origin Proof**：`{{origin_proof}}`\n\n**Mock Used**：`{{mock_used}}`{{fallback_reason_block}}\n\n**Policy**：`{{policy_version}}`"
    },
    {
      "tag": "hr"
    },
    {
      "tag": "markdown",
      "content": "{{summary_md}}"
    },
    {
      "tag": "action",
      "actions": [
        {
          "tag": "button",
          "text": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "打开 Trace" },
          "type": "primary",
          "url": "{{trace_url}}"
        },
        {
          "tag": "button",
          "text": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "复制 Trace ID" },
          "type": "default",
          "value": { "action": "copy_trace_id", "trace_id": "{{trace_id}}" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tag": "note",
      "elements": [
        {
          "tag": "plain_text",
          "content": "Thin-Agent：飞书侧仅转发与展示；所有决策与治理在 LiYe OS 内完成。"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
